{"tid":1307223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲升學 幫到就幫","createTime":"2019-07-11T12:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T21:02:25.000Z","uid":266777,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"432dc367ff19be2be87bf66c4eb7f23f7c461053","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"見到有英國既巴打開post<br />\n<br />\n咁唔爭在開個澳洲升學<br />\n如果各位巴絲有興趣到澳洲升學 我可以盡可能幫你地解答<br />\n我喺墨爾本住左十二年<br />\n原本係純文科出身 （當年A Level 中史 History Geography)<br />\n而家喺墨爾本某醫院既ICU做護士<br />\n所以 條條大路通羅馬<br />\nDSE既同學仔 唔好灰心 之後努力返少少 頭上就另有一片天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae501e50c600d5488c7e7a4680dc11e011b2948e","tid":1307223,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"係唔係住Bh？"},{"pid":"0a802e5c69ff57fe7b7905cd07f14852cdcb30f7","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae501e50c600d5488c7e7a4680dc11e011b2948e","tid":1307223,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:17:01.000Z","msg":"係唔係住Bh？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"唔係 但我熟BH <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc49395edd82e58c1bebad70b254ab132884cae","tid":1307223,"uid":175965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"有無聽過SAE學院？"},{"pid":"77ef02c8b9363703fc60c59d9aea840988552409","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc49395edd82e58c1bebad70b254ab132884cae","tid":1307223,"uid":175965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:24:33.000Z","msg":"有無聽過SAE學院？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"第一次聽 應該係原本base喺Queensland <br />\n但悉尼 墨爾本 同塔斯曼尼亞 有campus"},{"pid":"2853c76b0d522e1603fb052e5ec929d82ed495e6","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77ef02c8b9363703fc60c59d9aea84098