f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你打得咁detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想問下去4個月洗費大概幾多到？正常3餐 間中落下club咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身吾大洗"},{"pid":"e1e3c0c70f73ea041ffe260ec48b47208d601df7","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3664327e40fa664c8f5a9398b85a32688ddb4547","tid":1307223,"uid":255447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59fd3cbdebba7e71b3fd938c3c7464caa8134b59","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"83bf6b0f6a099415324d03f949b86d54859cd6ce","tid":1307223,"uid":255447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去exchange 想問QUT系唔系一個好選擇？我讀Business既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:01:02.000Z","msg":"如果你之後係一心返香港搵工，最好搵間係澳洲 &ldquo;Group of 8&rdquo; 既大學<br />\nThe University of Western Australia<br />\nThe University of Melbourne <br />\nMonash University (Melbourne)<br />\nUNSW Sydney <br />\nAustralian National University (Canberra)<br />\nThe University of Queensland <br />\nThe University of Adelaide <br />\nThe University of Sydney <br />\n<br />\n佢地係澳洲主流大學 多fundings 做research<br />\n設備配套冇得輸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:07:47.000Z","msg":"原來澳洲都有八大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你打得咁detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想問下去4個月洗費大概幾多到？正常3餐 間中落下club咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身吾大洗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"唔洗客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你預返一餐AUD15-20<br />\n平既AUD10都有 如果你鍾意去超市買野食<br />\n水電煤三個月交一次 約一人AUD300-400蚊<br />\n有啲分租屋既可能包埋水電煤<br />\n淨租既 睇下你係住咩區 可以好大分別 你最好問返住Queensland既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個月大概AUD2500-3000應該食同住都好好<br />\nOn campus 既一定係貴 所以去住 share house一定平啲"},{"pid":"784053ff6531315bbaa63bda11b385efb442f3b1","tid":1307223,"uid":156070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:18:26.000Z","msg":"monash 讀書風氣係咪唔好？聽人講冇乜本地學生讀 幾乎全部都係亞洲人"},{"pid":"3d4db2b1e83a60979302930b1c7821b14cec0302","tid":1307223,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係隔離問過 唔爭在係呢邊問埋la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟今年23, 非三大 CHEM grad (cpga ~3.2)<br />\n想出國讀d專業既科目轉field<br />\n心水有dietetics同physiotherapy<br />\n<br />\ndietetics 我搵過好多master 都好似唔係好收純chem, 要有bio related底<br />\nphysiotherapy 就更加係<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇機會報physiotherapy既2nd degree? 就算要經foundation我都ok <br />\ndietetics就比較想直接搵master讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意到有d premaster既班唔知有冇機會接駁上去"},{"pid":"fd06a4b9a05073ff6d33c46f76da38ff1ab598ed","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4db2b1e83a60979302930b1c7821b14cec0302","tid":1307223,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係隔離問過 唔爭在係呢邊問埋la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟今年23, 非三大 CHEM grad (cpga ~3.2)<br />\n想出國讀d專業既科目轉field<br />\n心水有dietetics同physiotherapy<br />\n<br />\ndietetics 我搵過好多master 都好似唔係好收純chem, 要有bio related底<br />\nphysiotherapy 就更加係<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇機會報physiotherapy既2nd degree? 就算要經foundation我都ok <br />\ndietetics就比較想直接搵master讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意到有d premaster既班唔知有冇機會接駁上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"如果你係舖路日後返香港做野<br />\n你要問埋香港洗唔洗再考牌<br />\n喺澳洲讀physio 係比較易搵工<br />\nDietitian 比較難<br />\n而你已經有一個chem degree<br />\n入澳洲既大學讀以上其中一科應該唔難<br />\nDietetics 係會比較容易入<br />\nPhysio 既course 入面都會要你讀返 anatomy and physiology, 所以冇問題<br />\n唔洗讀foundation!"},{"pid":"4cbc6e31cfa80f358766c2444528c9919c782675","tid":1307223,"uid":14188,"l