9-07-13T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"請問你bachelor係邊到讀?"},{"pid":"ab956d352cc8bdd74cfefc07c6ec75913840ed8f","tid":1307223,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd06a4b9a05073ff6d33c46f76da38ff1ab598ed","tid":1307223,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d4db2b1e83a60979302930b1c7821b14cec0302","tid":1307223,"uid":104423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係隔離問過 唔爭在係呢邊問埋la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟今年23, 非三大 CHEM grad (cpga ~3.2)<br />\n想出國讀d專業既科目轉field<br />\n心水有dietetics同physiotherapy<br />\n<br />\ndietetics 我搵過好多master 都好似唔係好收純chem, 要有bio related底<br />\nphysiotherapy 就更加係<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇機會報physiotherapy既2nd degree? 就算要經foundation我都ok <br />\ndietetics就比較想直接搵master讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留意到有d premaster既班唔知有冇機會接駁上去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T23:10:26.000Z","msg":"如果你係舖路日後返香港做野<br />\n你要問埋香港洗唔洗再考牌<br />\n喺澳洲讀physio 係比較易搵工<br />\nDietitian 比較難<br />\n而你已經有一個chem degree<br />\n入澳洲既大學讀以上其中一科應該唔難<br />\nDietetics 係會比較容易入<br />\nPhysio 既course 入面都會要你讀返 anatomy and physiology, 所以冇問題<br />\n唔洗讀foundation!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T10:43:24.000Z","msg":"thanks a lot <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d9dceae61e786f9dc636fb82c4b3b514b49b39","tid":1307223,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4fbe0dfde260e3e33182b362d0d51dcc4f6092c","tid":1307223,"uid":156258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1d9dceae61e786f9dc636fb82c4b3b514b49b39","tid":1307223,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1d9de89b75a22964acab3b71364e34cab7284b4","tid":1307223,"uid":156258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af78da78c36059a971df2f4b6d6250daa39e046","t